8373661: Address review feedback

- Fixed code style issues
- Added additional test case

Thanks to @RogerRiggs for the feedback.

8373661: Add edge case tests for Objects.requireNonNull methods

Added comprehensive edge case tests to improve test coverage:
- requireNonNull with null Supplier parameter
- requireNonNull with Supplier throwing exception
- requireNonNullElse with both arguments null
- requireNonNullElseGet with null supplier
- requireNonNullElseGet with supplier returning null

All new tests verify correct exception messages as per API specification.
